of what you have.

17:11.690 --> 17:14.694
What does it feel like

17:14.730 --> 17:17.369
to take a life?

17:17.400 --> 17:19.596
You seem a good man, Henry.

17:19.630 --> 17:23.031
Be thankful that you don't know.

17:23.069 --> 17:25.539
