21:45.030 --> 21:48.193
Yes.
Yes, you surely do.

21:48.240 --> 21:51.164
Whenever you got stuck
talking boating with my dad

21:51.210 --> 21:54.180
or modern dance
with my roommate,

21:54.210 --> 21:56.804
you'd be polite
and tap your glass

21:56.840 --> 21:59.741
