28:51.760 --> 28:53.626
Ah!
Mm-mm, no.

28:53.660 --> 28:55.128
Why do you think
I brought two of them?

28:55.160 --> 28:57.652
Each one gives a little,
everyone goes home happy.

28:57.700 --> 28:59.623
