32:54.170 --> 32:57.538
- Give me a little credit.
- Oh, God.

32:57.570 --> 33:00.665
I am done!
I don't care what you do to me.

33:00.710 --> 33:02.678
I am never gonna be like you.

33:02.710 --> 33:04.007
[chuckling]

33:04.050 --> 33:07.600
It's cute when you act
like you have a choice.

33:07.650 --> 33:09.709
The only path you take

33:09.750 --> 33:12.515
