33:51.730 --> 33:53.755
What?

33:56.930 --> 33:59.524
[sighing]

33:59.570 --> 34:01.231
What are you doing?

34:01.270 --> 34:02.760
Going back to sleep.

34:02.800 --> 34:05.007
Yeah, I can see that, but why?

34:05.040 --> 34:07.236
Because I'm tired.

34:07.270 --> 34:09.931
Mm, you're warm.

34:11.510 --> 34:14.719
And since you're more
screwed up than I am,

34:14.750 --> 34:16.878
what are you gonna do...

34:16.920 --> 34:19.581
judge me?

34:19.620 --> 34:22.590
<i>*Xk</i>

34:47.510 --> 34:50.514
[birds chirping]

34:58.260 --> 35:00.126
[gasps]

35:00.160 --> 35:03.130
[panting]

35:07.700 --> 35:10.533
