Casualty Clearing Station 54.

35:22.880 --> 35:25.110
What did you do to me?

35:28.120 --> 35:30.760
I used them.

35:30.790 --> 35:33.782
I used them to make us better.

35:39.670 --> 35:42.139
Oh, and Henry,

35:44.910 --> 35:47.333
[struggling]

35:47.370 --> 35:49.532
I saved you some.

35:52.380 --> 35:53.370
What are you talking about?

35:53.410 --> 35:54.445
Come, now.

35:54.480 --> 35:57.518
You said that you wanted
to know what it was like.

35:57.550 --> 36:00.144
You went to sleep weak,
and you woke up strong.

36:00.190 --> 36:03.182
Now, it's gonna take
some getting used to.

36:05.360 --> 36:08.022
[whispering]
What do you want me to do?

36:08.060 --> 36:10.620
Henry...

36:10.660 --> 36:12.924
He's wounded,
and he's suffering,

36:12.970 --> 36:15.962
and he's going to die anyway.

36:18.440 --> 36:21.432
Just this once.
[crows cawing]

36:25.980 --> 36:29.109
I told you I can't kill men.

36:30.080 --> 36:32.242
I know.

36:33.520 --> 36:36.512
But, that was before you met me.

36:55.340 --> 36:58.310
[suspenseful music plays *]

37:16.830 --> 37:19.720
So, this is what it's like being
part of a well-oiled machine.

37:19.770 --> 37:20.862
Suren must be happy.

37:20.900 --> 37:23.062
I have my own reasons.

37:23.100 --> 37:24.807
You did all this for me.

37:24.840 --> 37:27.468
You haven't eaten.
You must be starving!

37:27.510 --> 37:29.808
- Let's get some brekkie.
- You do whatever you want. I'm out.

37:29.840 --> 37:32.150
Come on, this is the best
I've felt in decades.

37:32.180 --> 37:34.547
It'll be like old times.

37:36.920 --> 37:38.649
Hey, I'm Josh.

37:38.690 --> 37:40.715
We met yesterday.

37:40.750 --> 37:42.582
Thanks for the invite.

37:44.760 --> 37:46.728
You're Henry.

37:46.760 --> 37:48.751
You look so much better.

37:52.130 --> 37:54.838
Catch you later, Aidan.

37:58.940 --> 38:02.137
Only one thing would
make him heal that fast.

38:02.180 --> 38:04.478
What happened in there?

38:10.480 --> 38:13.450
<i>*Xk</i>

38:15.260 --> 38:18.184
[panting]

38:18.220 --> 38:21.155
No, please, no.
Okay, you can do this.

38:21.190 --> 38:23.659
Cleansing breaths.

38:27.570 --> 38:29.493
Nick.

38:29.540 --> 38:30.894
Nick, you shouldn't
be here right now.

38:30.940 --> 38:32.010
Zoe told me what happened.

38:32.040 --> 38:34.202
I didn't know that
he was gonna kill them, Nick!

38:34.240 --> 38:37.107
- Who would kill them?
- The Reaper!

38:37.140 --> 38:40.440
Look, either you help me salt
us in, or you get out of here.

38:40.480 --> 38:41.641
- It's okay.
- You need to get out!

38:41.680 --> 38:43.819
It's okay.
We're gonna get you help.

38:43.850 --> 38:45.716
And then, you are never
gonna do this again.

38:45.750 --> 38:47.445
I didn't do anything!

38:47.490 --> 38:49.151
I didn't do anything!
It was him!

38:49.190 --> 38:51.056
Sally!

38:51.090 --> 38:54.025
There is no Reaper.

38:54.060 --> 38:57.052
<i>*Xk</i>

38:59.870 --> 39:02.362
I know I screwed up,
but I never brought it here.

39:02.400 --> 39:03.663
He didn't have anyplace to go.

39:03.700 --> 39:05.737
You know how many places I've
got where there's no pretense?

39:05.770 --> 39:08.137
Where just being
isn't exhausting?

39:08.170 --> 39:10.935
One.
This house, with you and Sally.

39:10.980 --> 39:12.869
I've almost earned
my freedom once and for all,

39:12.910 --> 39:14.309
but I told you
that it was gonna get messy.

39:14.350 --> 39:15.340
No, no, no, no.

39:15.380 --> 39:16.916
There's messy,
and then there's this.

39:16.950 --> 39:18.349
This is never going
to happen again.

39:18.390 --> 39:19.915
We're gonna get it back
to the way it was.

39:19.950 --> 39:21.042
Don't worry about it.

39:21.090 --> 39:24.981
- He's right behind you.
- No, there is nobody else here.

39:25.030 --> 39:26.327
- He's right behind...
- It's gonna be all right.

39:26.360 --> 39:28.419
- [screaming]
- Let go of him!

39:28.460 --> 39:30.098
He didn't do anything!

39:30.130 --> 39:33.521
He thinks he can have a human,
flaunt it in our face?

39:33.570 --> 39:34.731
Please, don't do this.

39:34.770 --> 39:36.465
Stop it!
Stop!

39:36.500 --> 39:39.470
I'm not gonna do this.
I'm never gonna be like you.

39:39.510 --> 39:40.932
[chuckling]

39:40.970 --> 39:44.076
Don't you get it, Sally?

39:44.110 --> 39:46.101
You are me.

39:46.850 --> 39:48.340
Here's how it goes.

39:48.380 --> 39:50.269
Usually, a ghost is around

39:50.320 --> 39:53.017
just long enough
to have a little fun.

39:53.050 --> 39:56.054
But the longer a ghost circles
the drain, crazier the ghost.

39:56.090 --> 39:58.525
What do you want?!

39:58.560 --> 39:59.721
[screaming]

39:59.760 --> 40:01.421
- I'm unbalanced?
- Yes!

40:01.460 --> 40:04.100
You're the one who passed up
your door, and you possess!

40:04.130 --> 40:06.861
I don't need your help!
You're crazy!

40:06.900 --> 40:09.790
[grunting]

40:09.840 --> 40:10.762
Who are you?

40:10.800 --> 40:12.609
[distorted]
You know exactly who I am.

40:12.640 --> 40:15.735
Sally!
There is no Reaper.

40:17.480 --> 40:20.472
[grunting]

40:20.510 --> 40:23.047
You are an interesting case,
Sally Malik.

40:23.080 --> 40:25.788
- What do you mean?
- You're...

40:25.820 --> 40:27.117
special.

40:27.150 --> 40:30.085
You really think so?

40:34.030 --> 40:35.259
Sally.

40:36.360 --> 40:37.896
Sally!

40:37.930 --> 40:40.069
Sally, Sally.
Let him go.

40:40.100 --> 40:41.420
You don't wanna do this, Sally.

40:41.470 --> 40:43.438
I think I do.

40:43.470 --> 40:45.234
Oh, and, boys,

40:45.270 --> 40:48.501
Sally isn't here anymore.

40:48.540 --> 40:50.030
[screaming]

40:54.850 --> 40:56.648
What did you do?

40:56.680 --> 40:59.012
He had to go.

40:59.050 --> 41:00.211
They all did.

41:00.250 --> 41:02.082
You don't get to decide that.

41:02.120 --> 41:04.179
Somebody has to.

41:04.220 --> 41:08.498
Somebody has to tell them that
they don't belong here anymore,

41:08.530 --> 41:10.999
that it's time
to stop holding on.

41:11.030 --> 41:13.829
Sally, you belong here with us.

41:13.870 --> 41:16.692
[deep voice]
Oh, that's so sweet.

41:16.740 --> 41:19.459
You sound just like Nick.

41:19.510 --> 41:22.502
Is that how you want
to be treated?

41:22.540 --> 41:25.475
[screaming]

41:32.790 --> 41:35.657
Aidan!
She's not kidding around, man!

41:37.060 --> 41:38.357
[grunting]

41:43.260 --> 41:46.264
<i>*Xk</i>

42:12.330 --> 42:13.479
[softly]
What's going on?

42:13.530 --> 42:16.522
We're not sure yet.

42:16.560 --> 42:18.562
Are-Are you, are you okay?

42:18.600 --> 42:21.570
I think...
[panting]

42:21.600 --> 42:24.968
I can't...

42:25.010 --> 42:27.536
Can you, um...
- Yeah.

42:27.570 --> 42:29.072
Of course.
- No, no.

42:29.110 --> 42:32.045
- What?
- Uh-uh, mm-mm.

42:32.080 --> 42:35.015
Guys, let me out.

42:35.050 --> 42:37.109
Guys, come on.

42:37.150 --> 42:39.710
[deep voice] I said let me
the hell out of here!

42:40.890 --> 42:43.916
<i>*Xk</i>
